title: E92 Survivalism
itunes:title: Survivalism
description:
In this episode, the team discusses survivalism with associate professor in Literature at American University and author of the novels "The Hive" and "Flood", Melissa Scholes Young.

Follow Melissa on Instagram @MelissaScholesYoung and go to her link tree at linktr.ee/melissascholesyoung for links to her books and other helpful resources.
